<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="1583de04-86be-4b2d-bcd6-4118f9d84a2d" >

    <h4>Reference&nbsp;</h4> 
<ul> 
 <li><a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/revenue-agency/services/benefits/recovery-benefit.html" target="_blank">Canada Recovery Benefit<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a></li> 
 <li><a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/revenue-agency/services/benefits/recovery-benefit/crb-how-apply.html" target="_blank">CRB - How to Apply<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a></li> 
</ul>
    





