                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1602783845192-mortgage-payment-deferral" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#aa93d6d6-7931-41f1-9982-d8fd3cf757c2" href="#accordion-content-1602783845192-mortgage-payment-deferral" aria-controls="accordion-content-1602783845192-mortgage-payment-deferral" aria-expanded="false">
                            Mortgage Payment Deferral
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1602783845192-mortgage-payment-deferral" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1602783845192-mortgage-payment-deferral">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1602783845192 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="c8a64372-009f-480c-84fc-613c67b9f770" >

    <h4>What is It?</h4> 
<p>For homeowners facing financial hardship from COVID-19 (like unemployment or reduced employment), their mortgage payments can be deferred for up to 6 months.</p> 
<h4>Am I Eligible?</h4> 
<p>Your lender - either your bank or your mortgage professional - can tell you if you are eligible for a mortgage payment deferral. Typically, the agreement indicates that you and your lender have agreed to pause or suspend your mortgage payments for a certain amount of time.</p> 
<h4>How Do I Claim It?</h4> 
<p>Contact your mortgage lender to create a deferral agreement. Please note that you will have to repay the amounts of the skipped payments, including both the principal and interest, once the agreement has come to an end. The agreement does not cancel, erase, or eliminate the deferred payments.</p> 
<h4>Reference</h4> 
<ul> 
 <li><a href="https://www.cmhc-schl.gc.ca/en/finance-and-investing/mortgage-loan-insurance/the-resource/covid19-understanding-mortgage-payment-deferral" target="_blank">COVID-19 - Mortgage Payment Deferral<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a></li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#c8a64372-009f-480c-84fc-613c67b9f770");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
