                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1592411827009-ontario-emergency-assistance" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#8a8857b8-0941-4ca2-9dca-7efda1184327" href="#accordion-content-1592411827009-ontario-emergency-assistance" aria-controls="accordion-content-1592411827009-ontario-emergency-assistance" aria-expanded="false">
                            Ontario Emergency Assistance
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1592411827009-ontario-emergency-assistance" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1592411827009-ontario-emergency-assistance">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1592411827009 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="5a72b14f-5a36-43e1-8e8e-986aaa462605" >

    <h4>What is it?</h4> 
<p>Emergency financial assistance for Ontarians in a crisis or emergency situation.</p> 
<p>Provides $733 for a month (more if you have children) for those requiring assistance with food or shelter costs.</p> 
<p>Support can last up to 48 days depending on the situation.</p> 
<h4>Am I Eligible?</h4> 
<p>Applicants must be in a crisis or emergency situation. This includes:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Being affected by COVID-19;</li> 
 <li>Facing eviction;</li> 
 <li>In or leaving an abusive relationship; or</li> 
 <li>Worried about your safety</li> 
</ul> 
<p>Ontarians getting assistance from Ontario Works or the Ontario Disability Support Program do not qualify.</p> 
<h4>How do I claim it?</h4> 
<p>Apply online via the&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ontario.ca/page/covid-19-support-people" target="_blank">Ontario Government website<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a>.</p> 
<h4>Reference</h4> 
<ul> 
 <li><a href="https://www.ontario.ca/page/apply-emergency-assistance">Ontario Emergency Assistance<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a>&nbsp;(<a href="https://news.ontario.ca/opo/en/2020/03/changes-to-ontarios-emergency-assistance-program-in-response-to-covid-19.html">News release<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a>)</li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#5a72b14f-5a36-43e1-8e8e-986aaa462605");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1592411827020-top-up-to-ontario-works--ow--and-ontario-disability-support-program--odsp-" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#8a8857b8-0941-4ca2-9dca-7efda1184327" href="#accordion-content-1592411827020-top-up-to-ontario-works--ow--and-ontario-disability-support-program--odsp-" aria-controls="accordion-content-1592411827020-top-up-to-ontario-works--ow--and-ontario-disability-support-program--odsp-" aria-expanded="false">
                            Top up to Ontario Works (OW) and Ontario Disability Support Program (ODSP)
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1592411827020-top-up-to-ontario-works--ow--and-ontario-disability-support-program--odsp-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1592411827020-top-up-to-ontario-works--ow--and-ontario-disability-support-program--odsp-">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1592411827020 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="8aa4f105-0dac-4386-b111-dd662af8d309" >

    <h4>What is it?</h4> 
<p>Additional financial assistance for those currently receiving social assistance and are facing additional costs related to COVID-19.</p> 
<p>Additional $100 for single individuals, $200 for families.</p> 
<h4>Am I Eligible?</h4> 
<p>Must be a current recipient of OW or ODSP.</p> 
<h4>How do I claim it?</h4> 
<p>Apply by calling your <a href="http://www.officelocator.mcss.gov.on.ca/?lang=en" target="_blank">local Ontario Works office<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a> Caseworker.<br> <br> Visit the <a href="https://www.mcss.gov.on.ca/en/mcss/" target="_blank">Ministry of Community Services website <span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a>for more details.</p> 
<h4>Reference</h4> 
<ul> 
 <li><a href="https://www.mcss.gov.on.ca/en/mcss/">Ministry of Community and Social Services<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a></li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#8aa4f105-0dac-4386-b111-dd662af8d309");});</script></div>

