    <h4>What is Changing?</h4> 
<ul> 
 <li>Double the CSG for all eligible full-time students up to $6,000, and up to $3,600 for part-time students in 2020-2021.</li> 
 <li>CSG-PD (permanent disability) and CSG for students with dependents would also be doubled to $4,000, up from $2,000.</li> 
</ul>
    





